obj_root_law:
  slug the-academy-of-scientific-and-innovative-research-act-2011
  handle (2110)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Academy of Scientific and Innovative Research Act, 2011`
  actNumber (13)
  enactmentDate 2012-02-06
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2110`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `वैज्ञानिक और प्रवर्तित अनुसंधान अकादमीअधिनियम, 2011`
  actYear (2012)
  ministry `Ministry of Science and Technology`
  department `Department of Secientific and Industrial Research`
  longTitle `An Act to establish an Academy for furtherance of the advancement of learning and prosecution of research in the field of science and technology in association with Council of Scientific and Industrial Research and to declare the institution known as the Academy of Scientific and Innovative Research, to be an institution of national importance to provide for its incorporation and matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate 03-04-2012
  notification `3rd April, 2012 (except sub-section (2) of section 5), vide notification No. S.O. 709(E), dated 2nd April, 2012, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii). 26th June, 2013 (sub-sec. (2) of section 5), vide notification No. S.O. 1850(E), dated 26th June, 2013, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii).`
  fetchedAt `2026-05-09T16:23:09.425Z`
  translations obj_root_law_translations
